title: The World's Largest Mouth | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 33
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


The babes are back and talking falling off a diet! Being on camera for a living means you get to watch your weight go up and down over the years. Shout out the Carvelanche! Who is the true king of the ice cream industry? The babes are starting a coffee company YASSSSS! The oldest living man is tryna take Kane Tanaka crown! Who is the oldest living couple? High School stories from the BABES! Best senior pranks. The babes talk about their days in detention. The worlds largest mouth! WOW!


Rate us on iTunes!
